{"tid":1819682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎，一宗死亡個案","createTime":"2020-01-11T04:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T05:24:27.000Z","uid":290443,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c73de4168975ef19af3caa213284fe26fb148d1d","tid":1819682,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"武漢市衛健委通報不明原因病毒性肺炎情況，指出在病原體初步判定為新型冠狀病毒之後，初步診斷有41宗病例，其中一宗死亡，兩宗已出院、7宗重症，其餘患者病情穩定；所有密切接觸者共739人，其中419人為醫務人員，已接受醫學觀察，沒有發現相關病例。<br />\n<br />\n衛健委又說，自本月3日以來，未發現新病例，目前未發現醫務人員感染，未發現明確的人傳人證據，武漢市將繼續加強治療患者、進行流行病學調查。<br />\n<br />\n衛健委指出，調查發現患者主要為武漢市華南海鮮批發市場的經營及採購人員，本月1日已對市場採取休市措施，並對全市公共場所，特別是農貿市場，進一步加強疾控指導和環境衛生管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502198-20200111.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502198-20200111.htm&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=98d12300\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502198-20200111.htm&h=2be178f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502198-20200111.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出街仲係無咩人戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fecd8f7dc19790a7ad6fcb41be59e826b5d0e3","tid":1819682,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b0876196d96c059c29df712b923b90ee076ed9a","tid":1819682,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9812c5b6880fec05c597fe44781d18955bb045ea","tid":1819682,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1709abde130fd7f81f41e4bc14dab88824b0ccf2","tid":1819682,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"